org.emocha.model
Class Preferences

java.lang.Object
  org.emocha.model.Preferences

public class Preferences
extends java.lang.Object

Preferences class is to configure all the information of the mobile device. Such as identifying the advice, connecting to remote server, setting and getting the device password, etc.
